{"tid":53781,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"第一次去北海道","createTime":"2016-12-25T03:43:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-03T09:08:14.000Z","uid":66220,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4c30ef368cdb0d3ee0b0dcbf48cbcf1e31a5e0ab","tid":53781,"uid":66220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T03:43:55.000Z","msg":"黎緊1月9號會去北海道自由行 機票同酒店一早就訂好左.行程都plan好.<br />\n<br />\n最近睇新聞話因爲大雪好多航班延誤 唔係就飛羽田去唔到札幌<br />\n<br />\n小弟plan行程果陣完全無諗過呢點 想問去開北海道既巴打們一月係咪因為落雪成日出現航班延誤 ？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n行程  <br />\n<br />\nday1 登別<br />\nday2 登別<br />\nday3 札幌<br />\nday4 札幌<br />\nday5 小樽<br />\nday6 滑雪 地點未搵<br />\nday7 香港<br />\n<br />\n我搭7:55班機直航 到時有延誤我就會無左第一晚溫泉旅館<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實咁plan有無問題 因為而家酒店仲可以改 。好迷惘求指點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">最多影多d靚相番黎比你地睇</span>"},{"pid":"7f66b4c6ea8b001cd7857cd5978f382fce57a105","tid":53781,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T03:45:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaf68db58e0dc943c96f345a1ee44217d086db72","tid":53781,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T03:46:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dea2a830b1699bdd7bdcea641caa780d8ddd3ba6","tid":53781,"uid":66220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T03:47:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自己渣車？？</blockquote><br />\n唔打算渣啦 無雪地開車經驗"},{"pid":"1784aa94d4637296e67729dd20abe9d1d70f8c0a","tid":53781,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T03:54:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5c97cb0412dccc5ab771e66a3e4a79d1e81e6846","tid":53781,"uid":9410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T03:55:54.000Z","msg":"去得落雪地方就要早D買定旅保，睇清楚條款<br />\n買D如果延誤包晒食住賠償既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到時去唔到咪claim囉，根本北海道大雪delay 係常有既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n至於會唔會延誤去唔到，求神拜佛架咋喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你都控制唔到，不過我通常唔會咁趕第一日就撲去第二到"},{"pid":"b71527500030f83050526b4731a5ca1ab8bfbaf5","tid":53781,"uid":9410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T03:57:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>自己渣車？？</blockquote><br />\n唔打算渣啦 無雪地開車經驗</blockquote><br />\n有冇諗住買北海道JR pass</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n岩呀，落雪無渣開唔建議渣車<br />\n佢行程得登別同滑雪地方有機會用，應該維唔到皮喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8ce3417a854b3038c96f394e07486df24e82901","tid":53781,"uid":66220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T03:59:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>自己渣車？？</blockquote><br />\n唔打算渣啦 無雪地開車經驗</blockquote><br />\n有冇諗住買北海道JR pass</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我去既地方唔多 目前剩係諗到買小樽pass"},{"pid":"e8a7b7324efbf2361bbdf7ed94fac3a4e9eeb46e","tid":53781,"uid":38351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T04:00:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去得落雪地方就要早D買定旅保，睇清楚條款<br />\n買D如果延誤包晒食住賠償既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到時去唔到咪claim囉，根本北海道大雪delay 係常有既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n至於會唔會延誤去唔到，求神拜佛架咋喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你都控制唔到，不過我通常唔會咁趕第一日就撲去第二到</blockquote><br />\nagger <br />\n而且賠償一般係賠已買咗飛嘅交通 &amp; 已俾錢嘅住宿開支/ 因延誤幾多個鐘而敷生嘅住宿開支。<br />\n記得要留意條款，多數只限延誤;因此 改行程引致嘅費用唔包。"},{"pid":"90eaf75b34dfd029120f002abb2aec094d5dda9d","tid":53781,"uid":66220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T04:06:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>去得落雪地方就要早D買定旅保，睇清楚條款<br />\n買D如果延誤包晒食住賠償既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到時去唔到咪claim囉，根本北海道大雪delay 係常有既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n至於會唔會延誤去唔到，求神拜佛架咋喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你都控制唔到，不過我通常唔會咁趕第一日就撲去第二到</blockquote><br />\nagger <br />\n而且賠償一般係賠已買咗飛嘅交通 &amp;amp; 已俾錢嘅住宿開支/ 因延誤幾多個鐘而敷生嘅住宿開支。<br />\n記得要留意條款，多數只限延誤;因此 改行程引致嘅費用唔包。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講還講 旅保都好似未買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0abe3e0793c85bfffd9d666157e77fc50af7c60","tid":53781,"uid":14227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T05:31:25.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 31號去<br />\n買左匯豐旅保 是咪伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"342ffffd1833eb5fdc3bfd4a99ed270794753c04","tid":53781,"uid":66220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T08:23:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 31號去<br />\n買左匯豐旅保 是咪伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n清 可以分享一下行程？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ecaea38db997d3d4d02ece8dd4c4fa1d13cd37f","tid":53781,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T09:42:38.000Z","msg":"day 6 見議你落旭山動物園玩一日都實際過滑一日雪。"},{"pid":"10aaea670e39cecef132b9481c8a1ef7c5335eb7","tid":53781,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T09:46:01.000Z","msg":"同埋第一日最好 stay 札幌都好過直入登別，去到都天黑冇左一日，入溫泉旅館應該擺向中間。"},{"pid":"cbba5cf731cb8d841cd5dd9942beb4a9e7b26794","tid":53781,"uid":20222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T10:01:13.000Z","msg":"前一日係小樽下一日應該一係去天狗山一係去札幌國際滑雪"},{"pid":"b8378ff71fcf5c5e7fd265850d36b0095f811434","tid":53781,"uid":40387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T10:12:53.000Z","msg":"1日滑雪，體驗下都ok ge<br />\n係札幌市有幾個近郊滑雪場，可以去體驗下，未學過最好搵個老師教（有識英文嘅，唔哂驚濕撚哂）<br />\n如果硬膠膠咩都唔識想滑雪，但又唔請老師，就註定呢個運動將會同你無緣⋯⋯因為唔易學架"},{"pid":"cb7f161d226909eceb578f4fb22c6791f122289c","tid":53781,"uid":66220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T11:18:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1日滑雪，體驗下都ok ge<br />\n係札幌市有幾個近郊滑雪場，可以去體驗下，未學過最好搵個老師教（有識英文嘅，唔哂驚濕撚哂）<br />\n如果硬膠膠咩都唔識想滑雪，但又唔請老師，就註定呢個運動將會同你無緣⋯⋯因為唔易學架</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n諗住去札幌國際滑雪場 太靚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 話知仆死都底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd431f8f27dac170be59a7bd454236c14cda7c41","tid":53781,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T12:25:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ead8900ea185a6c2226443cee45c00692162ad6b","tid":53781,"uid":14227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T13:00:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 31號去<br />\n買左匯豐旅保 是咪伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n清 可以分享一下行程？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n頭兩日去東京<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n登別 札榥 小樽 旭川 層雲峽 星野渡假村<br />\n每個地方一兩日到 是咪好tight <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92f8f997a6012d8bd46553589cdba0568e03fb3f","tid":53781,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T13:29:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 31號去<br />\n買左匯豐旅保 是咪伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n清 可以分享一下行程？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n頭兩日去東京<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n登別 札榥 小樽 旭川 層雲峽 星野渡假村<br />\n每個地方一兩日到 是咪好tight <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n北海道星野已經可以完全用普通話溝通。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54ce8cbe037b18ce743d428a1a3712116a8c38f2","tid":53781,"uid":67878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T15:12:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1b99c6c60002570b238200e7d3ab5340e3c94254","tid":53781,"uid":2300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T16:05:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 31號去<br />\n買左匯豐旅保 是咪伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nhsbc 唔差但貴"},{"pid":"67803efd4e36f0bc2d5b791a662d66973dbbecb2","tid":53781,"uid":14227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T05:24:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 31號去<br />\n買左匯豐旅保 是咪伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nhsbc 唔差但貴</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔買都買左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 見一次半次就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23e4d815beb35286e63bbbcabac04027dc639ea8","tid":53781,"uid":11019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T05:28:13.000Z","msg":"小樽一定玩唔到一日"},{"pid":"a13fadaa